   "source": [
    "# Root Left Right"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "3eb1ef7f",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def preorder(node):\n",
    "    if node.left==None:\n",
    "        return \n",
    "    print(node.val)\n",
    "    preorder(node.left)\n",
    "    preorder(node.right)\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "80b1f3eb",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "**Time complexity is O(n) and spcae complexity if O(height) which is stack space used due to recursion involved in our code.**"
   ]
  },
